PPP_Analyzer
Class clsRunSuperHirn

java.lang.Object
  PPP_Analyzer.clsRunSuperHirn

public class clsRunSuperHirn
extends java.lang.Object

Class to executes label-free qunatification workflow for PASS. This include the SuperHirn processing (feature extraction, ms2 to ms1 mapping, LC-MS alignment, etc.), integration of SuperHirn XML results into PASS database, tandem2pepXML conversion and finally data cleanup: - Commands runSuperHirn: feature extraction of an mzXML input file - Commands runSuperHirnDBPusher: parsing and importing of SuperHirn results into PASS database - Commands runCleanUp...: clean up (deletion) of intermediate files - etc.

Author:
Lukas N. Mueller
